# File Locks for Parallel Work

# Format: filepath|agent-id|timestamp|reason
# Example: src/index.ts|agent-a|2026-01-24T12:00:00Z|registering new tool

# Current locks (empty = no locks)
# Add your lock here when working on a shared file
# Remove your lock when done

# High-conflict files that require locking:
# - src/index.ts (MCP server entry point)
# - package.json (dependencies)
# - README.md (main documentation)
# - src/utils/types.ts (shared types)
